text: Motion
Motion
Hehe...

Tenka, you seem to be having fun.
What are you looking at?

Ah...
Producer-san...

Right now...
I was searching online...for rewards...!

Sleeping aids...
Tenka wonders, if there are any good ones...

Sleep aids, huh?
That sounds nice...!

Yeah...!
There are so many neat things...!

By the way,
what kind of options are you considering?

Um...
things like this... and...

(...A hammock, or an oversized cushion...
They're all quite large items...)

Ah, and...
like the idea of an indoor tent...!

I-I see...
─But, Tenka...

Are such large items...
going to fit in your room?
──Huh?

...I-I didn't think about...
the size of Tenka's room...
...Haha...
Augh...

...I'll ask...
Mom and Dad... if there's anywhere to put them...
